<body>
    <h1>Task 11 - RAD</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"84ce7d997458" id=3D"Task11-RAD-1.Introduction">1. I=
ntroduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"44ebee76621d" id=3D"Task11-RAD-1.1Purpose">1.1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"c91c89fb6e85">The purpose of this document is to define the =
requirements for deploying the Bookstore API application on AWS using a two=
-tier architecture.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c68ec79dffd2">The document is intended for DevOps engineers,=
 developers, and project stakeholders who are responsible for deploying, ma=
naging, and testing the cloud infrastructure.</p>
<p local-id=3D"afe7dde271d6">This document outlines the functional and non-=
functional requirements required to successfully deploy the FastAPI applica=
tion and configure a secure database connection.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"fae6d2c22df4">
<h2 local-id=3D"ab4760c1d640" id=3D"Task11-RAD-1.2Scope">1.2 Scope</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8bed6472562a">The scope of this project includes deploying t=
he Bookstore API application and its database using a two-tier architecture=
.</p>
<p local-id=3D"74551a0a66a1">The deployment includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8778800bdfe5">
<li local-id=3D"f72af827036c">
<p local-id=3D"080be1842cd4">Hosting the FastAPI application on an AWS EC2 =
instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"78253cc03683">
<p local-id=3D"2e170ae0cc39">Using <strong>MongoDB Atlas</strong> as the ma=
naged database service</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6cb211321621">
<p local-id=3D"804236ac8801">Configuring secure communication between the a=
pplication server and the database</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"82d32f311451">
<p local-id=3D"568dbaf504fd">Configuring network access and security settin=
gs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fdf4b47d57c3">
<p local-id=3D"5b2c29cc40b0">Verifying API functionality through database r=
ead/write operations</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"011a3be3fb36">The project does <strong>not include productio=
n-level scaling, CI/CD automation, or advanced monitoring systems</strong>,=
 as the deployment is intended for internal development and testing.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"3fa62d623913">
<h2 local-id=3D"e51126d668fb" id=3D"Task11-RAD-1.3Definitions,Acronyms,andA=
bbreviations">1.3 Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbreviations</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"58=
b0f2c0-6d1e-4704-9321-50ac7f2eb098" class=3D"confluenceTable">
