<hr local-id=3D"ddc4c43bde40">
<h2 local-id=3D"f3995444e0ea" id=3D"Task11-RAD-1.4References">1.4 Reference=
s</h2>
<p local-id=3D"e315dd5ec840">GitHub Repository<br><a href=3D"https://github=
.com/pushkar-iamops/bookstore-api" local-id=3D"9f01002c9c2e" data-card-appe=
arance=3D"inline" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://github.c=
om/pushkar-iamops/bookstore-api</a></p>
<p local-id=3D"5de63bc9885f">AWS Documentation<br><a href=3D"https://docs.a=
ws.amazon.com" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://docs.aws.am=
azon.com</a></p>
<p local-id=3D"cbf25f05c897">FastAPI Documentation<br><a href=3D"https://fa=
stapi.tiangolo.com" local-id=3D"4deeb7eebd25" data-card-appearance=3D"inlin=
e" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://fastapi.tiangolo.com</a=
></p>
<p local-id=3D"e29db6c4c177">MongoDB Documentation<br><a href=3D"https://ww=
w.mongodb.com/docs" local-id=3D"832b8cc2c09c" data-card-appearance=3D"inlin=
e" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://www.mongodb.com/docs</a=
></p>
<hr local-id=3D"0e3ba40c31ec">
<h2 local-id=3D"21f0dbba19aa" id=3D"Task11-RAD-1.5Overview">1.5 Overview</h=
2>
<p local-id=3D"83a45281fd94">This document is structured into multiple sect=
ions describing the system requirements and architecture.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e6a786897766">
<li local-id=3D"14ca38620b18">
<p local-id=3D"10c242f18d9a">Section 1 introduces the purpose and scope of =
the document.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f1b3857a9fc3">
<p local-id=3D"04a6dd2f28f9">Section 2 provides an overview of the project =
objectives and background.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c72a1dcf6684">
<p local-id=3D"24e0e7ea5194">Section 3 describes the functional requirement=
s and use cases.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"907ac938bfe0">
<p local-id=3D"bdd9f7b5086e">Section 4 lists the non-functional requirement=
s including security and performance.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3d23446ee061">
<p local-id=3D"1b0bd962743a">Section 5 discusses assumptions and dependenci=
es.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e374caa7bc92">
<p local-id=3D"3a03ee89022b">Section 6 provides a risk analysis for the pro=
ject.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e5a33440ed40">
<h1 local-id=3D"1031f05dac88" id=3D"Task11-RAD-2.ProjectOverview">2. Projec=
t Overview</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"8babcdf12e0b" id=3D"Task11-RAD-2.1ProjectObjectives">2.1 Pr=
oject Objectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"0db4bf8d141d">The main objectives of this project are:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7f992cabb2fd">
<li local-id=3D"c339c929aa7e">
<p local-id=3D"cac7c10de62e">Deploy the Bookstore API application on AWS.</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e3f99e5fcb4b">
<p local-id=3D"e0fa160e4ef3">Implement a <strong>two-tier architecture sepa=
rating application and database layers</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b6972517a76f">
<p local-id=3D"44607d3de10f">Configure a secure connection between the Fast=
API application and MongoDB Atlas.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"12c9a4ea1a20">
<p local-id=3D"fe988993d242">Ensure the API is accessible for development a=
nd testing.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e60aaf630abd">
<p local-id=3D"9f103459aab8">Verify that the application can successfully r=
ead and write data to the database.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9db82942f2c9">
<h2 local-id=3D"93fc33904ae3" id=3D"Task11-RAD-2.2BusinessGoals">2.2 Busine=
ss Goals</h2>
<p local-id=3D"9029e43f20ee">The business goals of this deployment include:=
</p>
<ul local-id=3D"61c529576ee3">
<li local-id=3D"489caad4706d">
<p local-id=3D"d38cc4f38edf">Creating a secure testing environment for inte=
rnal development</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0193604d1ced">
<p local-id=3D"f18a5dfd7dc1">Demonstrating proper cloud architecture practi=
ces</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"33252cb8c097">
<p local-id=3D"1d8346672716">Ensuring separation of concerns between applic=
ation and database layers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"03e37cd59046">
<p local-id=3D"e79a496b4cd9">Providing a scalable cloud-based infrastructur=
e for future development</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"7fc0d19800f8">
<h2 local-id=3D"569085bee64b" id=3D"Task11-RAD-2.3Background">2.3 Backgroun=
d</h2>
<p local-id=3D"dbf65b614fe8">ABC Technologies requires a cloud-based deploy=
ment for its Bookstore API service used for internal testing and developmen=
t.</p>
<p local-id=3D"2509d340fb48">The application is developed using <strong>Fas=
tAPI</strong>, a modern Python framework for building APIs. The backend dat=
abase uses <strong>MongoDB Atlas</strong>, which is a fully managed NoSQL d=
atabase platform.</p>
<p local-id=3D"79f966330288">To maintain proper architecture and security, =
the system follows a <strong>two-tier architecture</strong>, where:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"3d0f002ab079">
<li local-id=3D"412b339f19bc">
<p local-id=3D"061c7c5c62cc">The <strong>application layer runs on AWS EC2<=
/strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"26d69527570f">
<p local-id=3D"c8c2013b45e2">The <strong>database layer is hosted on MongoD=
B Atlas</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"204f13296100">This architecture improves maintainability, se=
curity, and scalability compared to running both services on the same serve=
r.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"02c8fd1450c5">
<h2 local-id=3D"829065539dbb" id=3D"Task11-RAD-2.4Constraints">2.4 Constrai=
nts</h2>
<p local-id=3D"29f0e8a231c4">The following constraints apply to the project=
:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c18dd9a09066">
<li local-id=3D"68842233d0d2">
<p local-id=3D"9ecf072f1e15">Deployment must be completed within <strong>3 =
hours</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4e7db83fad78">
<p local-id=3D"77f78f29c1ec">Infrastructure must be hosted on <strong>AWS</=
strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c1aa8a4cfe3f">
<p local-id=3D"7951265f8cc3">Database credentials must not be stored in app=
lication code</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a0638ccc6b32">
<p local-id=3D"16dd688bb4c5">Security groups must restrict unauthorized acc=
ess</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e9066c9604d">
<p local-id=3D"76426bab33c5">The system is intended only for <strong>develo=
pment and testing</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"49babd734fc5">
<h1 local-id=3D"b9f288988b20" id=3D"Task11-RAD-3.FunctionalRequirements">3.=
 Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"143686933c4e" id=3D"Task11-RAD-3.1UseCaseDiagram">3.1 Use C=
ase Diagram</h2>
<p local-id=3D"c7194231e955">The use case diagram illustrates interactions =
between the <strong>DevOps Engineer</strong> and the system components invo=
lved in deploying and configuring the application infrastructure.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5b5df29f6c56">The diagram represents the following activitie=
s:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"bd18315bb1e3">
<li local-id=3D"739b80fa4e10">
<p local-id=3D"81619b9ab3e3">Deploying the application server</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"93b280e14e41">
<p local-id=3D"0f03b9a91983">Setting up the MongoDB Atlas database</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4122ba5b1f47">
<p local-id=3D"4985aac10fe3">Configuring application-database connectivity<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"35c630c88a57">
<p local-id=3D"ba521b69df84">Testing API functionality</p></li>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image ima=
ge-center" alt=3D"Untitled Diagram.drawio (10)-20260311-090213.png" width=
=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"e92bd70688f198cc33bca3dff5b993fc0d2ea6aeb7=
c7460a07e0a2f282b1cfa8" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki=
/download/attachments/1844215829/Untitled%20Diagram.drawio%20(10)-20260311-=
090213.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1773220016408&amp;cacheVersio=
n=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"526" data-width=3D"917" data-unresolved-=
comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1852473348" data-linked-reso=
urce-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-res=
ource-default-alias=3D"Untitled Diagram.drawio (10)-20260311-090213.png" da=
ta-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-cont=
ent-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1844215829" dat=
a-linked-resource-container-version=3D"3" data-media-id=3D"4a61ab9e-d50f-40=
10-bf47-883ac978e7bf" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"268"></span>
<hr local-id=3D"37e86531b079">
<h1 local-id=3D"70b915b21d2d" id=3D"Task11-RAD-3.2UseCases">3.2 Use Cases</=
h1>
<hr local-id=3D"3b5cd06cd3ff">
<h1 local-id=3D"9ca548a8c099" id=3D"Task11-RAD-3.2.1UseCase1:DeployApplicat=
ionServer">3.2.1 Use Case 1: Deploy Application Server</h1>
<p local-id=3D"4b4263da71f7"><strong>Description</strong><br>
Deploy the FastAPI application on an AWS EC2 instance.</p>
<p local-id=3D"7ef787a9dc38"><strong>Actors</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"a84e1182115e"><strong>Preconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"f20537302226">
<li local-id=3D"748cc9a05662">
<p local-id=3D"beb16163cc53">AWS account access is available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4efe2ca108fe">
<p local-id=3D"09ac6b0e30cf">EC2 instance permissions are configured</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"6e7a1fc54b1e">
<p local-id=3D"74bb5ada6a8f">Internet connectivity is available</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"07979f492520"><strong>Postconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"31ba507085e3">
<li local-id=3D"6b338bf68b86">
<p local-id=3D"28bc5a081f29">FastAPI application is running on the EC2 inst=
ance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0cd6c6ee0c2e">
<p local-id=3D"41488343624a">Application is accessible via public IP and po=
rt</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"9da9e1aaab85"><strong>Flow of Events</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"a8a6cd632222">
<li local-id=3D"fe5c707d7191">
<p local-id=3D"11671b0ebeca">Launch an EC2 instance.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"098930f0b418">
<p local-id=3D"654ec174e00b">Connect to the instance using SSH.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"239c4c3cda9d">
<p local-id=3D"f1b1dbf4a6d7">Install Python and required dependencies.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"c39fff1eedd6">
<p local-id=3D"544bc3f50e02">Clone the application repository from GitHub.<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a07aff6303ef">
<p local-id=3D"b5933c72d162">Install project dependencies.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3ca5fb8ce19f">
<p local-id=3D"64022bb6510d">Start the FastAPI application.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"24b24af6bce3"><strong>Alternative Flows</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"e4985cb0a42f">
<li local-id=3D"a1f58c72ee90">
<p local-id=3D"be67ca916905">Dependency installation fails =E2=86=92 reinst=
all dependencies.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fe77fddd66e4">
<p local-id=3D"4e2faa4aaa31">Application fails to start =E2=86=92 review lo=
gs and configuration.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"0f4eddecbe48">
<h1 local-id=3D"880545641c06" id=3D"Task11-RAD-3.2.2UseCase2:SetupMongoDBAt=
lasDatabase">3.2.2 Use Case 2: Setup MongoDB Atlas Database</h1>
<p local-id=3D"eb80d64c97e5"><strong>Description</strong><br>
Provision and configure a MongoDB database using MongoDB Atlas to serve as =
the backend database for the application.</p>
<p local-id=3D"dc43ca4ba7c3"><strong>Actors</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"08c127d318b0"><strong>Preconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"82dbfacece71">
<li local-id=3D"c61d9ea35585">
<p local-id=3D"686dd2e426e6">MongoDB Atlas account is available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d0807a0cc6c0">
<p local-id=3D"48abe672d8c2">Internet connectivity is available</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"2246aa15bd9e"><strong>Postconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"9577ab3bd656">
<li local-id=3D"95f05413381b">
<p local-id=3D"7639fe2d0912">MongoDB Atlas cluster is running</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f9a0cf1f3df4">
<p local-id=3D"16a1744ce314">Database credentials are configured</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ad9c28ff11ac">
<p local-id=3D"0aa0ddef8b1e">Application server can connect to the database=
</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"61bdfcaf6f3a"><strong>Flow of Events</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"88db52f4b1a7">
<li local-id=3D"f1cee7b1a1d5">
<p local-id=3D"d662e59a9d00">Log in to the MongoDB Atlas console.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d730467add83">
<p local-id=3D"3654271c9599">Create a new cluster.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c1d7a716a2c0">
<p local-id=3D"dc4b0e74bf95">Configure database user credentials.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"71b409215715">
<p local-id=3D"6f9dd54118bd">Configure IP access rules.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f566a86f923d">
<p local-id=3D"bebfbd8c92e1">Obtain the database connection string.</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"76e7449577de">
<p local-id=3D"6869b08ade48">Verify that the cluster is active.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"dd8e485cb5d8"><strong>Alternative Flows</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"5b367f0e4ba9">
<li local-id=3D"8a11f31388ba">
<p local-id=3D"4ca39f1e3702">Database connection failure =E2=86=92 verify I=
P access configuration.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"12e8e27742ee">
<h1 local-id=3D"cad313133179" id=3D"Task11-RAD-3.2.3UseCase3:ConfigureAppli=
cation-DatabaseIntegration">3.2.3 Use Case 3: Configure Application-Databas=
e Integration</h1>
<p local-id=3D"a631c6f93cb7"><strong>Description</strong><br>
Configure the FastAPI application to connect to the MongoDB Atlas database.=
</p>
<p local-id=3D"c9e042a50ec2"><strong>Actors</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"da8c9b8b6c98"><strong>Preconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"dd5a86a84045">
<li local-id=3D"ba0fd314a483">
<p local-id=3D"18d18a6e0b90">Application server is running</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1881cbf5ba31">
<p local-id=3D"a1b68e3817ea">MongoDB Atlas database is available</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"bf12742d1948"><strong>Postconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"f611bc057b44">
<li local-id=3D"e1c3902e08c5">
<p local-id=3D"e59db7e49d8e">Application can communicate with the database<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"21f8414573fa"><strong>Flow of Events</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"bcf6f0618ef7">
<li local-id=3D"b532151cb8d2">
<p local-id=3D"5651d82e4864">Obtain the MongoDB Atlas connection string.</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"5d56ca3a0611">
<p local-id=3D"8e8a28381b72">Store the connection string using environment =
variables.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e717e1e0e947">
<p local-id=3D"abff55f24391">Update the application configuration.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"384b5cfe9e5d">
<p local-id=3D"0769664d94a0">Restart the FastAPI application.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3a159ff0d51d">
<p local-id=3D"3c6249174db2">Verify successful database connectivity.</p></=
li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"a509c7d75452"><strong>Alternative Flows</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a63c3fd00a06">
<li local-id=3D"728f8bd23a12">
<p local-id=3D"063824c405ac">Incorrect credentials =E2=86=92 update environ=
ment variables.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"0eea7ae80de2">
<h1 local-id=3D"ad5845bda843" id=3D"Task11-RAD-3.2.4UseCase4:VerifyAPIFunct=
ionality">3.2.4 Use Case 4: Verify API Functionality</h1>
<p local-id=3D"deea1c7b5795"><strong>Description</strong><br>
Test API endpoints to confirm successful database interaction.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a6a131b92429"><strong>Actors</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"629be695c792"><strong>Preconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"706f2e02fb9c">
<li local-id=3D"e4c4e40b0c9b">
<p local-id=3D"459ed0ebc083">Application and database are running</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"eedc4d5d6cea"><strong>Postconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"71634ecf55d9">
<li local-id=3D"fef8974cbde5">
<p local-id=3D"79b8b130aff9">API successfully performs read and write opera=
tions</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8ddee5cb9700"><strong>Flow of Events</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"36d183923b4c">
<li local-id=3D"ae41640eb642">
<p local-id=3D"dc3cb448e7c7">Access API endpoints using a browser or API cl=
ient.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e7b0cae206d6">
<p local-id=3D"8dc15cf1203f">Send test API requests.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fc72db461ed6">
<p local-id=3D"2477aa1811bc">Verify database records are created or retriev=
ed.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"baef97cc18fa"><strong>Alternative Flows</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"6937056a9d21">
<li local-id=3D"24d10cd6c5fe">
<p local-id=3D"ad1b131aa30d">API errors occur =E2=86=92 check logs and data=
base connectivity.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"23201bfc5cbf">
<h1 local-id=3D"60b961e91ac9" id=3D"Task11-RAD-4.Non-FunctionalRequirements=
">4. Non-Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"4e6fa4616eae" id=3D"Task11-RAD-4.1PerformanceRequirements">=
4.1 Performance Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"5852d31116b3">
<li local-id=3D"cecaad6abbb0">
<p local-id=3D"68f84e6dfce4">API response time should remain under <strong>=
2 seconds</strong> for testing requests.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c0379cba9b59">
<p local-id=3D"63c39f474d5c">The system should handle multiple concurrent t=
est requests.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"26d3b1ab04ce">
<h2 local-id=3D"4f0760903dd1" id=3D"Task11-RAD-4.2SecurityRequirements">4.2=
 Security Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"c3ed9ff99e6f">
<li local-id=3D"348e5b8406a9">
<p local-id=3D"4e957c2c7727">Database credentials must not be stored in app=
lication code.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f4d5cca61317">
<p local-id=3D"bed58228309c">Environment variables must be used for databas=
e configuration.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7e6f94595055">
<p local-id=3D"35e8987015a6">AWS security groups must restrict unauthorized=
 access.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8327c456b541">
<p local-id=3D"6c247345197c">Database access must be controlled using Mongo=
DB Atlas network access rules.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"4709f0ebb778">
<h2 local-id=3D"2e5a0a8aa958" id=3D"Task11-RAD-4.3UsabilityRequirements">4.=
3 Usability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"7b0ffbec0047">
<li local-id=3D"b84b5d0c39ca">
<p local-id=3D"f896bb5dbe7c">The API must be accessible via public IP and d=
esignated port.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8cdf0372799b">
<p local-id=3D"4a58c065c862">API documentation should be available through =
the FastAPI documentation interface.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9f2d82e7083c">
<h2 local-id=3D"0a9a4ed26d8d" id=3D"Task11-RAD-4.4ReliabilityRequirements">=
4.4 Reliability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"21694bd820d0">
<li local-id=3D"155f6fabcc9c">
<p local-id=3D"6d960a580dfe">Application and database services must remain =
operational during testing.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"931a25b4722d">
<p local-id=3D"2f7cf368d158">The system should allow restart of services wi=
thout losing data.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"c92c09c463a5">
<h2 local-id=3D"f1ad36c6aed8" id=3D"Task11-RAD-4.5ComplianceRequirements">4=
.5 Compliance Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"d6440d03ea1c">
<li local-id=3D"d88cdb5ff3ee">
<p local-id=3D"ae9774ead48c">Follow AWS security best practices.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"42caa5a6871e">
<p local-id=3D"264af7a8939a">Protect database credentials and sensitive con=
figuration.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d4ccce3efe73">
<h1 local-id=3D"e8d52260defd" id=3D"Task11-RAD-5.AssumptionsandDependencies=
">5. Assumptions and Dependencies</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"90a30ef38001" id=3D"Task11-RAD-5.1Assumptions">5.1 Assumpti=
ons</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"3bb1d3c62f53">
<li local-id=3D"341ddd7d9879">
<p local-id=3D"10ce4b07acd3">AWS services are available and accessible.</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"972e7dc127db">
<p local-id=3D"7847085cf996">The GitHub repository is accessible.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"92f04997234f">
<p local-id=3D"ea5e3e4740a2">MongoDB Atlas services are operational.</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9612fb3584d9">
<h2 local-id=3D"6035dfaa42d4" id=3D"Task11-RAD-5.2Dependencies">5.2 Depende=
ncies</h2>
<p local-id=3D"dbea4a3efb7f">The project depends on the following systems:<=
/p>
<ul local-id=3D"449db3364d1e">
<li local-id=3D"336f79b4be53">
<p local-id=3D"971ea88f66e9">AWS EC2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0176f4365643">
<p local-id=3D"7e1c0cba789d">GitHub repository availability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c3ddd3976ce6">
<p local-id=3D"65e75f5fd0c1">Python runtime environment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a7e6cc89cc4e">
<p local-id=3D"a13ead0472d9"><strong>MongoDB Atlas</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"038664f55a03">
